The King of Torts is a legal/suspense novel written by American author John Grisham. The first edition (ISBN 0-385-50804-2) was published in hardcover format by Doubleday in 2003, and immediately debuted at #1 on the New York Times Best Sellers list, remaining in the top 15 for over twenty weeks. Dell Publishing published the paperback edition later in 2003 (ISBN 0-440-24153-7).